<div class="block-contributor">
		

		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><span class="smallcaps"><strong>Deborah Y. Abramson</strong></span> lives in Boston, Massachusetts, and is enrolled in the MFA program in creative nonfiction at Goucher College. Her work has appeared in the <em>Boston Phoenix</em> and <em>Metropolis</em>.</p><a href="/contributors/deborah-y-abramson" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
	</div>
</div>

